config SUBSYSTEM_COREDUMP
	tristate "Subsystem coredump driver"
	default n
	help
	  Say Y here if you want to enable the subsystem coredump driver.
	  Use APIs exported by this module to generate coredumps/crash info.

	  To compile this driver as a module, choose M here: the
	  module will be called sscoredump.
